                            <comment id="14905762" author="githubbot" created="Thu, 24 Sep 2015 03:19:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;GitHub user ChengXiangLi opened a pull request:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/1178&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/1178&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-2754&quot; title=&quot;FixedLengthRecordSorter can not write to output cross MemorySegments.&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FLINK-2754&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FLINK-2754&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; FixedLengthRecordSorter can not write to output cross MemorySegments.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    The issue happens while call FixedLengthRecordSorter::WriteToOutput with non-zero offset and write record across multi memory pages. Fix the issue and add more unit test.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You can merge this pull request into a Git repository by running:&lt;/p&gt;

